snippet.title: Supernormal - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: Inspired by Allison Road. SUPERNORMAL is a psychological horror game set in a seemingly ordinary apartment harbouring dark secrets. Play as Detective Wyatt, tasked with unravelling the unsettling disappearance of Masato Sakamoto's daughter. Search for clues and unravel the sinister truth. Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2532430/Supernormal
